OL,3,CNew Victims' Commissioner appointed
OL,4,Cfor Northern Ireland
OL,6,FA new Commissioner for Victims and
OL,7,FSurvivors for Northern Ireland has
OL,8,Fbeen appointed by the First and deputy
OL,9,FFirst Ministers.
OL,11,FJoe McVey will take up his post on
OL,12,FOctober 6 for a period of four years.
OL,14,FThe principle aim of the commissioner
OL,15,Fis to safeguard and promote the
OL,16,Finterests of victims and survivors.
