OL,3,CNew Victims' Commissioner appointed
OL,4,Cfor Northern Ireland
OL,6,FConfirming the appointment, First
OL,7,FMinister Michelle O'Neill said victims
OL,8,Fand survivors deserve a "strong,
OL,9,Findependent voice to ensure their
OL,10,Fneeds are recognised and prioritised,
OL,11,Fand it is vital that we continue to do
OL,12,Fall we can to support them".
OL,14,FShe added: "We are confident that Joe
OL,15,FMcVey will be a dedicated champion and
OL,16,Fpowerful advocate for the rights and
OL,17,Fneeds of all those who have suffered."
