OL,3,CNew Victims' Commissioner appointed
OL,4,Cfor Northern Ireland
OL,6,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,7,FPengelly added: "Ensuring that the
OL,8,Fneeds of victims and survivors is at
OL,9,Fthe heart of our trauma-informed,
OL,10,Fvictim-centred service is the key
OL,11,Fcomponent to this vital work.
OL,13,F"I wish Joe all the best in his new
OL,14,Frole as commissioner as he works to
OL,15,Fensure that the voices of our victims
OL,16,Fand survivors are heard loud and
OL,17,Fclear, and that they have access to
OL,18,Fthe highest quality mental and
OL,19,Fphysical wellbeing support."
