OL,3,CNew Victims' Commissioner appointed
OL,4,Cfor Northern Ireland
OL,6,FThe work of the commission is
OL,7,Fcategorised under three areas `
OL,8,Faddressing the past, effective service
OL,9,Fprovision and building towards a
OL,10,Fbetter and more reconciled future.
OL,12,FMr McVey is a former chief executive
OL,13,Fofficer of Brain Injury Matters BIM
OL,14,F(NI), a regional disability third-
OL,15,Fsector organisation supporting those
OL,16,Faffected by an acquired brain injury.
